titles.title: A resolution honoring former President William Jefferson Clinton on the occasion of his 58th birthday.
A resolution honoring former President William Jefferson Clinton on the occasion of his 58th birthday.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary:
(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)
Honors former President William Jefferson Clinton on the occasion of his 58th birthday on August 19, 2004, and extends best wishes to him and his family.
